</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5343753" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5343753" box="[137,1138,1968,1990]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5343753/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="649" startId="9.[137,172,1968,1990]" targetBox="[142,1476,317,1952]" targetPageId="9">
